# nixie asset pipeline: assets/base/ (masters + masks) and the generator
# scripts are source; assets/derived/ and non-shipped runtime staging dirs
# are regenerable build output (see assets/stage_assets.py). assets/runtime/nixie/
# IS tracked -- CMakeLists.txt installs it directly, no build step produces it.
__pycache__/
assets/derived/
assets/runtime/nixie-*/
assets/base/nixie-clock/*-DO-NOT-USE.png
